originalText.text:
I have been a patient of hers for the last 10 years.  And lately the doctors  way of practice and politeness has gone out the door. She literally stays in an appointment with you less than 5 minutes! Sometimes even less than 5 mins. I've actually timed it. What kind of doctor does that!
I recently moved 2 hrs away and was told to pay a copay when I see her for my follow up that's in 35 days from now. I was told by her nurse that I could call today for a cream for yeast infection due to antibiotics.  The doctor was rude to say ," tell the patient she has to come to her follow up first and pay me for a copay. Then I'll send her medicine to her pharmacy."  10 years of my life wasted with this ill mannered doctor!! If you want a real GYN go to an actual doctor not a nurse!
